'''Sandy Lick Creek''' is a [[tributary]] of [[Redbank Creek (Pennsylvania)|Redbank Creek]] in  northwest [[Pennsylvania]] in the [[United States]].

Sandy Lick Creek and the [[North Fork (Pennsylvania)|North Fork]] join to create Redbank Creek in the borough of [[Brookville, Pennsylvania|Brookville]], [[Jefferson County, Pennsylvania|Jefferson County]].

